Title: USB Rocket and Circus Cannon Launcher Controller
Description:
A library to control the Dream Cheeky USB Rocket Launcher and Circus Cannon. Also includes demo which has keyboard and Wiimote (Wii remote) support.

More info: http://www.kudzuworld.com/blogs/Tech/WiiRockets.aspx
